  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_tod_1819_rasgbi_tod145_sanad_r.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="raj" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>श्री <persName ref="#jalandharnath">जलंधरनाथ</persName> जी सत्य छै</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>Shri <persName ref="#jalandharnath">Jalandharnath</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref> is the truth</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="eng" type="laterAddition" rend="top centre">
            <p>To <unclear><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_mahajan">Mhajans [mahajans]</ref></unclear> of <placeName ref="#bhilwara">Bhilwara</placeName><note>This remark may have been added by <persName ref="#jamesTod">James Tod</persName>.</note></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="raj" type="authorisation" rend="middle centre">
            <p><lb rend="empty"/><stamp type="seal">
               <mentioned>
                  <lb/>॥ श्री ॥
                  <lb/>सिदेश्वर श्री <persName ref="#jalandharnath">जलधर 
                  <lb/>नाथ</persName> चरणसर<gap/> राज 
                  <lb/>राजेश्वर महाराजा धिराज 
                  <lb/>महाराजा श्री <persName ref="#manSinghMarwar">मांसिंह</persName> 
                  <lb/>जी <unclear>करपमुका </unclear>
               </mentioned></stamp>
            <lb rend="empty"/>
            <lb/><figure></figure></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3">
            <p><lb rend="empty"/><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal
               <mentioned>
                  <lb/>Shri
                  <lb/>The great ascetic Shri <persName ref="#jalandharnath">Jalandharnath</persName>
                  <lb/><gap/>The greatest king of kings,
                  <lb/>great king of kings
                  <lb/>Maharaja Shri <persName ref="#manSinghMarwar">Man Singh</persName>
                  <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref><gap/>
            </mentioned></stamp>
            <lb rend="empty"/>
               <lb/><figure><figDesc>A stylized drawing of a dagger</figDesc></figure></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="raj" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>॥ स्वारुप श्री राज राजेश्वर महाराजा धिरा-
               <lb/>ज महाराजा श्री <persName ref="#manSinghMarwar">मांनसिंघ</persName> जी वचनात 
               <lb/><placeName ref="#bhilwara">भीलाडा</placeName> रा महाजनां वोपारीयां दिसे
               <lb/>।तथा खातर जंमैं राख <placeName ref="#mundwa">मूंडवा</placeName> रै मेलै माल
               <lb/>जिंनस लेनै आवजो हासल मै अधक री
               <lb/>माफ हुसी ।सबत <date calendar="#samvat-shravanadi">१८७६ रा आसोज सुद १२</date>
               <lb/>मुकांम पायतखत <placeName ref="#jodhpurFort">गढ जोधपुर</placeName> 
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4">
            <p>
               <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarup">Sarup</ref> Shri Greatest of Kings, the Great King of Kings, 
               <lb/>Maharaja Shri <persName ref="#manSinghMarwar">Man Singh</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref> says
               <lb/>to the great merchants and traders of <placeName ref="#bhilwara">Bhil[w]ara</placeName>:
               <lb/>Thus, set your minds at ease. Bringing goods and
               <lb/>items, come to the <placeName ref="#mundwa">Mundwa</placeName> fair. From the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_hasal">hasal</ref>,
               <lb/>half will be forgiven. <date calendar="#samvat-shravanadi">Asoj [Ashwin] <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sudi">sudi</ref> 12 of the year 1876</date>.
               <lb/>Place: The foot of the throne [i.e., the royal capital], <placeName ref="#jodhpurFort">Fort Jodhpur</placeName>
            </p>
         </div>
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_tod_1819_rasgbi_tod145_sanad_v.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="raj" type="clericalNotes" rend="top centre">
            <p>।नकल लीवी श्री हजुर रै दफतर</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div5" corresp="#orig_div5">
            <p>Copy taken [in] the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_daftar">daftar</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_shriHuzur">Shri Huzur</ref>.</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="raj" type="invocation" rend="bottom centre">
            <p>॥ श्री ॥</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div6" corresp="#orig_div6">
            <p>Shri</p>
         </div>
         
      </body>
